# Cloudflare API token (used by scripts/setup-dns.sh to seed AWS Secrets Manager).
# The CloudClips-Dns CDK stack reads the token from Secrets Manager at deploy time —
# it is never baked into CloudFormation templates or Lambda environment variables.
#
# Create a token at https://dash.cloudflare.com/profile/api-tokens with:
#   - Zone / DNS / Edit permission for the sokech.com zone
CLOUDFLARE_TOKEN=YOUR_CLOUDFLARE_TOKEN_HERE